{"word":"πόθεν","slug":"πόθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πόϑεν</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ποῦ\">ποῦ</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ interrog.\">interrog.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a>, direct or indirect, regarding an answer to account for <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> on direction or source <b>from where, whence,</b> of place <b><a href='B:470 15:33'>Mt 15:33</a>; <a href='B:490 13:25'>Lk 13:25</a>; <a href='B:500 2:9'>J 2:9</a>; <a href='B:500 3:8'>3:8</a>; <a href='B:500 6:5'>6:5</a>; <a href='B:500 7:27'>7:27f</a>; <a href='B:500 8:14'>8:14</a>; <a href='B:500 9:29'>9:29f</a>; <a href='B:500 19:9'>19:9</a>; <a href='B:730 2:5'>Rv 2:5</a>; <a href='B:730 7:13'>7:13</a>;</b> of cause <b><a href='B:660 4:1'>Js 4:1</a>;</b> other <b><a href='B:470 13:27'>Mt 13:27</a>, <a href='B:470 13:54'>54</a>, <a href='B:470 13:56'>56</a>; <a href='B:470 21:25'>21:25</a>; <a href='B:480 6:2'>Mk 6:2</a>; <a href='B:490 20:7'>Lk 20:7</a>; <a href='B:500 4:11'>J 4:11</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> on manner <b>how is it that, how can it be that <a href='B:480 12:37'>Mk 12:37</a>; <a href='B:490 1:43'>Lk 1:43</a>; <a href='B:500 1:48'>J 1:48</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ποδονιπτήρ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ποιέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}